    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped sweet potato</strong> to a baking tray with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]</span><strong> vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give it a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 15-20 min or until the sweet potato is cooked and golden</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2073.-step-2-x200.jpg",
